item.description:
@runescape_sucks wrote:

Tutorial:

I don’t think anyone qualifies to state the game being terrible is a fact. I don’t think it is, but it just doesn’t satisfy me anymore. I started playing the game because it was unique, but that has changed in these past few months.

The only reason I don’t like it, is because it doesn’t feel like runescape anymore, I don’t like combat, specifically. Skilling is still okay.

Tutorial:

I don’t think anyone qualifies to state the game being terrible is a fact. I don’t think it is, but it just doesn’t satisfy me anymore. I started playing the game because it was unique, but that has changed in these past few months.

The game is now a bad rip off of many other mmorpgs, i’m not saying that is a bad idea. But they’ve done it in a very terrible way. World of warcraft for example is a successful game. How ever do they really think people who are interested in those type of games will join runescape? Let’s be honest now, the only people who join are 10 year olds. It’s probably also the reason why so many people are crying because their childhood just died. Bye
